description: When you want a memory card you can count on, every day, choose this for your electronic device designed for SD memory. They are fast, built to last, and ready when you are. Store high quality photos, videos, music and more with this high storage capacity (64 GB) and super speed performance Class 10. Important: Although this memory card is the same size and shape as regular SD card it can only be used by devices designed for SDXC - Extreme High Capacity device.
title: 64GB SD XC Class 10 SCT Secure Digital Ultimate Extreme Speed SDXC Flash Memory Card 64G 64 GIGS GB FOR Digital Camera SLR Tablet Computer GPS
